title: Match of the Day - 27th September 2014 - 720p50 X264
description:
SPORT: Match of the Day
On: BBC 1 HD    
Date: Saturday 27th September 2014 
Time: 22:30 to 00:05 

Gary Lineker introduces highlights of the day's eight Premier League fixtures, including two derby matches. Liverpool clash with Everton for the first Merseyside bragging rights of the season in the early kick-off. In the early-evening game, Arsenal host their north London neighbours Tottenham Hotspur. Plus champions Manchester City travel to Hull City while fellow title contenders Chelsea take on Aston Villa. In Saturday's other fixtures Manchester United face West Ham, Crystal Palace take on Leicester, Southampton meet QPR and Sunderland entertain Swansea.
